nodes.text: Mission to Tatooine  (Hunt for Jaesa Willsaam)

Around 3643 BBY, Darth Baras's apprentice was sent on a mission to the planet Tatooine to find Jedi Master Yonlach during their search for Nomen Karr's Padawan. The Sith apprentice found Yonlach's location and eliminated him along with his fellow Jedi Master Yul-Li.
